---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---
<MainLayout
  title="About KUEM"
  description="KUEM is an engineering-driven IoT solutions company focused on utility and infrastructure digitalization in the EU market."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container split">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Company</p>
        <h1>Engineering-driven IoT company focused on utilities and infrastructure.</h1>
        <p>
          KUEM combines field deployment experience, platform engineering, and integration expertise to deliver reliable
          IoT outcomes for utility and industrial operators.
        </p>
      </div>
      <article class="panel">
        <h2>What defines KUEM</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Strong specialization in smart metering and utility operations</li>
          <li>Nexavia platform for scalable deployment and integration</li>
          <li>EU market focus with region-specific operational knowledge</li>
          <li>Execution-oriented approach from pilot to rollout</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
